replies.body:
I know every one asks about their champ, but is there any minor rework plans for Fiora? Early game back side vitals are more punishing than rewarding, and being able to 1 v 1 mid/late game isn't too impressive because that's when team fights happen. 
Last season she was good for a while, but now that damage and mobility are super high, she doesn't fit into the game as well. 

